s this seem retarted to anyone else?<br>
Just got killed trying to do capt, twice.  Pulled to the beach near the rock like we have many times. Nothing in sight, fight going along nicely. Von warps right on our head out of nowhere and fluxes us all nicely raping us. Fairly annoyed at this we have a warrior kite the capt around for a bit while we get ressed and buffed. He runs near us and we tag off him and he runs off to zone the adds to DN. He had 2 dogs and a wurm on him I believe. Were fighting capt again, fight going along fine and wham... out of nowhere Glati warps on our heads and kills our clerics, captain poofs and dragons go on their marry way.<br>
Lovely...<br>
<br>
Now... this faction is for dragon alligned people. Quest gives you a positive +CoV hit when compelting it. You kill a bad giant which is on giant faction. So... why in the hell would dragons attack YOU when you're doing their quest? If anything, they should assist and attack the giants.<br>
Now, I understand. Adds challenge or whatever. But its not very challenging when random screwed up pathing causes dragons to warp right on top of you. Not only am I annoyed at screwy pathing but made me wonder why the hell dragons would assist captain in the first place. Done it before when there was a dragon pathing nearby, know how to harmony to avoid agro.<br>
<br>
Bleh, this capt attempt sucked bigtime :/ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utanilium.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tanilium</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 11:08:20 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> As I understand it was because the captain would fight the drakes/dragons...<br>
<br>
Hence, you could solo the quest.  Not easy, but doable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unotwen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>notwen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 11:39:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> 

Umm... that makes no sense.  They should just be faction neatral to each other if nothing else. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urykarderashken.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rykar Derashken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/2/01 12:49:11 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> Blame the fact that people exploited this quest by making the capt get worn down by roaming COV mobs.  Also blame Verant for not thinking that any druid/ranger worth their salt can single pull this guy anyway. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufogelxanedu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fogel Xanedu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/3/01 9:02:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> We just pull him in tunnel. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwandarone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WandarOne</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/3/01 9:59:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> /nod fogel....you get no adds in tunnel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uayashii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ayashii</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/3/01 10:21:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> Having the CoV faction mobs not attacking the capt doesn't mean the CoV faction mobs should assist the capt. Totally two different things. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualdelbertstiener.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aldelbert Stiener</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 2:26:42 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> I'm giant factioned &amp; the capt. scowls at me &amp; even attacked me once running to ToV.  Verant really needs to fix him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaraulthmarquet.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maraulth Marquet</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 8:46:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> The giants for Scout do not give faction anymore when killed and dragons will help them out when pulled. I used to be on giant faction and was top aligned with giants, they still conned ready to attack. I did the quest a short while ago with max ally to CoV now, and dragons assist him.<br>
<br>
Go figure... Verant's way of fixing things is to make a Dragon help a Giant... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhinterdir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>HinterDir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 9:30:08 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> just have the druid / ranger harmony anything that even looks in your direction.<br>
always worked for us in over 20 scout quests. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utanisemanasponge.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tanise Manasponge</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 1:18:16 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> Glati is the common add as her pathing sends her very close to the normal pull spot (&quot;safe&quot; rock). Von paths nearby but he seems to have a huge roam path because I'll see him once then not again for around an hour. Basically the best bet if you pull to &quot;safe&quot; rock is fight damn near on the rock. This is what I've been doing the last few times and so far no Glati add, though she gets close enough to say &quot;Oh C$%#&quot;. Also good to time the pull for when Glati is roaming away as her path, while not as long as Vons, still takes her a while. <br>
<br>
Tunnel pulling works except for the happy velious mobs falling under the world thingy. Had that happen twice. Naturally the GM you petition will have no clue of this bug and want to examine it further (maybe we should ask these no clue gms about Daoc =P). I myself have petitioned, reported, and feedbacked this bug twice now and I know several guildees and friends have as well. Verant knows about it but currently doesn't seem to give a C%$#. Besides it's a CoV aligned quest and we all know Verant hates CoV aligned peeps. =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urimidal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rimidal</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://homepages.ihug.co.nz/~lasovac/temp/pornstar.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 3:47:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> We DO harmony any dragon or roaming mob that we can even make out with max clip plane, but the dragon adds twice we didnt even see. Just warped right on top of our heads out of nowhere :/<br>
apparently the group that did scout before us failed because they had 3 dragons warp on top of them when capt was just about dead.<br>
