gimptastic <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uremfin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Remfin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/4/01 6:27:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dragons assisting Kromzek Captain in scout quest</span><hr size=1> We all know how Verant hates CoV people<br>
